# Debian XFCE Auto Login (LightDM)

This guide explains how to **skip the login ID/password screen** and enable **automatic login** on **Debian + XFCE** using **LightDM**.

> âš ï¸ Recommended for **personal desktop PCs only**.  
> Not recommended for laptops or shared computers due to security risks.

---

## âœ… Environment
- OS: Debian
- Desktop: XFCE
- Display Manager: LightDM
- Username: `rina`

---

